summary: Container image integration tests
description: |
    Deploys pre-built container images via docker-compose and verifies
    end-to-end workqueue functionality: enqueue, dispatch, reconcile,
    deduplication, priority ordering, admin API, and metrics.

    Images are set via environment variables (from Konflux Testing Farm):
      FACTORY_RECEIVER_IMAGE
      FACTORY_DISPATCHER_IMAGE
      FACTORY_ADMIN_IMAGE
      ECHO_RECONCILER_IMAGE

    For group snapshots, Testing Farm sets IMAGE_URL_<COMPONENT>.
    For single component snapshots, Testing Farm sets IMAGE_URL.
    Plan environment+ derives FACTORY_*_IMAGE from these.
test: bash tests/container/run.sh
duration: 15m
require:
    - docker
    - docker-compose
    - curl
    - python3
framework: shell

adjust+:
  - when: initiator == konflux
    enabled: true
  - when: initiator != konflux
    enabled: false
